  * audio/video pass-through -> can be used for muxing, tagging, chapter editing
  * a lot of option to automate stuff
 .
 This package contains the common files.

Package: hybrid-tools
Architecture: amd64 i386
Section: metapackages
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 aac-enc, aften,
 bdsup2sub++,
 dcaenc, delaycut, divx265,
 faac, flac, flvextract-python | flvextract | flvextractcl, ffmbc, ffmpeg,
 gpac,
 kvazaar,
 lame, lsdvd,
 mediainfo, mencoder, mkvtoolnix, mp4fpsmod, mplayer | mplayer2,
 neroaac,
 opus-tools,
 sox,
 telxcc, tsmuxer,
 vorbis-tools, vpx-tools,
 x264, x265
Description: Tools required by Hybrid
 This metapackage will install additional tools required by Hybrid:
 aac-enc, aften, bdsup2sub++, dcaenc, delaycut, divx265, faac, flac,
 flvextract-python or flvextract, ffmbc, ffmpeg, gpac (mp4box), kvazaar,
 lame, lsdvd, mediainfo, mencoder, mkvtoolnix, mp4fpsmod, mplayer or mplayer2,
 neroaac, opus-tools, sox, telxcc, tsmuxer, vorbis-tools (oggenc), vpx-tools,
 x264, x265.

